data.description: Highly desirable Adams floorplan #2265, with 2265 living square feet offering four bedrooms three bathrooms, upgraded kitchen with formica, all stainless appliances convey. Split floor plan with wonderful oversize master suite featuring walk-in shower and two sinks larger bedrooms can accompany larger furniture, enjoy all Florida entertaining on your covered oversized back patio, big backyard with plenty of room for pool. Neighboring properties have a fence, making a fenced in yard affordable and easy to complete. Why wait for a new construction when this nearly new home is available! All the hard work has been done, blinds are up appliances are in, lighting has been upgraded, hurry to purchase today.
